description: >-
  Apply private npm registry patterns for scoped packages. Use when modifying
  .npmrc, Dockerfiles with NPM_TOKEN, or adding private dependencies.
globs: '.npmrc, .docker/**/Dockerfile, compose.yaml, .env.example'
alwaysApply: false
tags:
  - docker
